{"word":"G4179 - πολλαπλασίων - pollaplasíōn - pol-lap-las-ee'-ohn - Manifold more","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πολλαπλασίων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pollaplasíōn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pol-lap-las-ee'-ohn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Manifold more</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அதிகமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"manifold, much more"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4183 - πολύς - polýs - pol-oos'/4183\">G4183</a> and probably a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4120 - πλέκω - plékō - plek'-o/4120\">G4120</a>; <i>manifold</i>, that is, (neuter as noun) <i>very much more:</i> - manifold more.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}